=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LinCongN_ex4 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark gritty sound, with square_like oscillator character around 284 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 284.4812
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.0025
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8739
  pitch_clarity: 149.2087
  inharmonicity: 0.5504
  type: square_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -24.3844
  resonance_freq: 301.4648

